{"id":417,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":19,"title":"19. Phone Out of Order (1)","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":10,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/19-phone-out-of-order-1.417/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/19-phone-out-of-order-1-2022-03-07-21-10-46/0-19-phone-out-of-order-1.mp3","transcript":"Hey! Hey!\nWhat's wrong?\nThere's something wrong with the phone. I'm getting a strange noise.\nAre you? I can hear you clearly.\nHello! Hello!\nThis pay phone might be out of order.\nI'll call you again with another phone....\nHello! How about now? Is there still a strange noise?\nYes. Perhaps my phone is out of order.\nYou should get in touch with the phone company.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:31","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hey! Hey!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/19-phone-out-of-order-1-2022-03-07-21-10-46/1.mp3","time_start":3.28,"time_end":4.58},{"position":2,"content":"What's wrong?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/19-phone-out-of-order-1-2022-03-07-21-10-46/2.mp3","time_start":4.58,"time_end":5.36},{"position":3,"content":"There's something wrong with the phone. I'm getting a strange noise.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/19-phone-out-of-order-1-2022-03-07-21-10-46/3.mp3","time_start":5.64,"time_end":8.65},{"position":4,"content":"Are you? I can hear you clearly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/19-phone-out-of-order-1-2022-03-07-21-10-46/4.mp3","time_start":8.65,"time_end":10.28},{"position":5,"content":"Hello! Hello!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/19-phone-out-of-order-1-2022-03-07-21-10-46/5.mp3","time_start":10.28,"time_end":11.88},{"position":6,"content":"This pay phone might be out of order.